name: 36 Days of Type || N // Nightcrawler (14/36)
description: Nightcrawler (Kurt Wagner) is a fictional superhero appearing in American comic books published by Marvel Comics, commonly in association with the X-Men. Created by writer Len Wein and artist Dave Cockrum, he debuted in the comic book Giant-Size X-Men #1 (May 1975).[1] The typeface used for Nightcrawler is Vampiro One.
